text: National Highway 160C, commonly referred to as NH 160C is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 60. NH-160C runs in the state of Maharashtra in India. == Route == NH160C connects Rahuri, and Shani Shingnapur in the state of Maharashtra. == Junctions == : Terminal near Rahuri. : Terminal near Shingnapur. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 160C on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Maharashtra
